c: 7
v: 26
t: "ya bani adam qad jaealna lakum lbasana ystr ewratkm, wahu libas aldrwrt, wlbasana llzynt waltjml, wahu min alkmal waltnem. wlbas taqwaa allah taealaa bifiel al'awamir wajtnab alnwahy hu khayr libas llmwmn. dhlk aldhy mann allah bih ealaykum min aldlayl ealaa rbwbyt allah taealaa wwhdanyth wfdlh warahmatuh bebadh; likay ttdhkru hadhih alnem, ftshkru lilah elyha. wafi dhlk amtnan min allah taealaa ealaa khalqh bhdhh alnem"